24:32.572 --> 24:33.737
Can you get the feed?
I'm trying!

24:33.739 --> 24:35.005
[<i> gunshots</i> ]

24:44.183 --> 24:45.716
Jake: Elise?

24:47.620 --> 24:48.819
You're gonna be okay, elise.

24:48.821 --> 24:49.720
[<i> camera shutter clicking</i> ]

24:50.556 --> 24:52.223
Hey.

24:52.225 --> 24:53.224
Elise.

24:53.226 --> 24:55.059
I shot him.

24:55.061 --> 24:56.760
You shot him.

24:56.762 --> 24:57.795
You're gonna be okay.

24:57.797 --> 24:58.963
You hear me?

24:58.965 --> 25:00.097
Stay with me, elise.

25:00.099 --> 25:02.199
[ breathing heavily ]

25:02.201 --> 25:03.667
[<i> camera shutter clicking</i> ]

25:03.669 --> 25:05.269
[ laughter ]

25:05.271 --> 25:06.971
This was your father?

25:06.973 --> 25:09.039
Yep, back when
he was a congressman.

25:09.041 --> 25:10.841
Had the whole place
in stitches.

25:10.843 --> 25:14.578
That's hilarious.

25:14.580 --> 25:16.981
Now, gentlemen...

25:16.983 --> 25:19.016
We all know
why i asked you here.

25:19.018 --> 25:20.784
I made a mistake...

25:20.786 --> 25:22.119
Betrayed
the people's trust...

25:22.121 --> 25:25.256
And, in doing so,
created a situation

25:25.258 --> 25:28.125
Where you can either support me
and risk looking like fools

25:28.127 --> 25:30.794
Or throw me under the bus
and help the democrats hang me.

25:30.796 --> 25:33.664
But as it's me who put you
in this position,

25:33.666 --> 25:36.800
I'm willing to offer some things
in exchange for your mercy.

25:36.802 --> 25:38.702
Now, steve,
i know you have a tight race

25:38.704 --> 25:40.004
Coming up in november.

25:40.006 --> 25:41.872
I'm prepared to stump hard
on your behalf

25:41.874 --> 25:43.741
And put my whole machine
behind your fundraising efforts.

25:43.743 --> 25:45.009
Elizabeth:
The president's also prepared

25:45.011 --> 25:46.143
To back the infrastructure bill,
senator.

25:46.145 --> 25:48.646
Even though there's
way too much pork

25:48.648 --> 25:50.848
Going to your cronies there
in wyoming, arnie.

25:50.850 --> 25:52.316
Liz will finalize
all the details.

25:52.318 --> 25:55.085
Now, unfortunately,
i do have a country to run,

25:55.087 --> 25:56.854
So as much
as i'd like to stay...

25:58.824 --> 26:01.191
Sit, mr. President.

26:01.193 --> 26:02.893
This has been fun.

26:02.895 --> 26:04.962
But as far
as i'm concerned,

26:04.964 --> 26:07.798
We're still at the foreplay
stage of the evening.

26:07.800 --> 26:09.900
The fun stuff
still lies ahead.

26:09.902 --> 26:11.569
So have yourself a seat

26:11.571 --> 26:18.175
And let's start talking
about the true cost of mercy.

26:19.178 --> 26:21.011
[<i> camera shutter clicking</i> ]

26:21.013 --> 26:23.647
♪♪

26:26.619 --> 26:29.286
This is preposterous.

26:29.288 --> 26:31.288
Well, we'll roll them back
in increments.

26:31.290 --> 26:33.190
That way there will be
less media attention.

26:33.192 --> 26:35.059
Equal pay?
The brandon bill?

26:35.061 --> 26:37.261
Those were huge legislative
achievements, senator.

26:37.263 --> 26:39.296
For the democrats.
Not for us.

26:39.298 --> 26:41.665
No. Absolutely not.

26:41.667 --> 26:45.669
Gentlemen, can we have
the room, please?

26:47.106 --> 26:48.872
That means you, too, liz.

26:50.643 --> 26:51.976
[ door opens ]

26:57.850 --> 26:59.917
Stanley,
this isn't politics.

26:59.919 --> 27:01.085
This is extortion.

27:01.087 --> 27:02.937
All right, how about this?

27:02.938 --> 27:04.788
How about i give you
equal pay? Hmm?

27:04.790 --> 27:06.323
I'll let you keep that.

27:06.324 --> 27:07.857
Arnie only put that in there,
i think,

27:07.860 --> 27:09.326
'cause his wife
is driving him bonkers.

27:09.328 --> 27:10.928
So that's yours.

27:10.930 --> 27:12.229
But in return for that favor,
though,

27:12.231 --> 27:14.965
I must insist
you give us the brandon bill.

27:14.967 --> 27:18.335
Stan, listen to me --
whatever you have to do
to kill those provisions --

27:18.337 --> 27:19.336
Executive order...

27:19.338 --> 27:20.804
I'm not gonna do that.

27:20.806 --> 27:22.206
I'm afraid
you don't have a choice.

27:22.208 --> 27:26.043
You know, i've had dalliances,
mr. President.

27:26.045 --> 27:27.111
We all have.

27:27.113 --> 27:29.380
Your problem is,
you got caught.

27:29.382 --> 27:32.316
And that's why it's you
on your knees in front of me

27:32.318 --> 27:33.717
Instead of the reverse.

27:33.719 --> 27:36.253
Kill the brandon bill.

27:36.255 --> 27:38.322
You made a lot of enemies
for us

27:38.324 --> 27:40.824
With the law and order community
passing that thing.

27:40.826 --> 27:42.359
If you could find
a way of quashing it,

27:42.361 --> 27:44.328
That would make
all the difference.

27:48.401 --> 27:50.668
Let me think about it.

27:50.670 --> 27:53.404
[ breathes deeply ]

27:53.406 --> 27:55.973
Oh, and, sir?

27:55.975 --> 27:59.276
Next time you decide to go
outside your marriage,

27:59.278 --> 28:01.278
Choose yourself a girl

28:01.280 --> 28:03.947
Who's a little more palatable
to the base.

28:06.686 --> 28:08.952
What is that
supposed to mean?

28:10.756 --> 28:12.856
Full roll-back
on the brandon bill,

28:12.858 --> 28:15.125
Or we start pursuing
impeachment.

28:15.127 --> 28:16.360
Sir.

28:16.362 --> 28:19.997
♪♪

28:19.999 --> 28:22.866
[ door opens, closes ]

28:26.772 --> 28:28.038
Friends say
pope's post-college years

28:28.040 --> 28:30.241
Were typical
of an urban 20-something --

28:30.242 --> 28:32.443
Scraping by, having fun,
and hustling to make her mark.

28:32.445 --> 28:35.045
Those hard times faded, though,

28:35.047 --> 28:37.815
Once pope
began dating older men.

28:37.817 --> 28:39.950
No doubt
drawn to her youth and beauty,

28:39.952 --> 28:42.953
The men shared not just the fact
that they were older,

28:42.955 --> 28:44.455
But they were powerful.

28:44.457 --> 28:46.056
Pope was even once engaged

28:46.058 --> 28:48.425
To senate majority leader
edison davis.

28:48.427 --> 28:51.762
Senator davis' office
refused comment for this piece.

28:51.764 --> 28:55.199
One thing that is certain is
that with each new relationship,

28:55.201 --> 28:57.201
Pope's profile increased

28:57.203 --> 29:00.003
Along with the power
of the subsequent suitor.

29:00.005 --> 29:04.341
Knowing this, is it any wonder
that pope would set her sights

29:04.343 --> 29:07.211
On the powerful man
on the planet?

29:07.213 --> 29:09.012
[<i> projector running</i> ]

29:12.518 --> 29:15.185
[ keyboard clacks ]

29:15.187 --> 29:17.821
[ cellphone rings ]

29:23.829 --> 29:25.062
[ cellphone beeps ]

29:25.064 --> 29:26.196
What?

29:26.198 --> 29:28.031
I need to talk to you.

29:28.033 --> 29:30.100
About the brandon bill.

29:30.101 --> 29:32.168
Did you know that
there's a porn version of us?

29:32.171 --> 29:34.404
Actually three, i think.

29:34.406 --> 29:35.873
Yeah.

29:35.875 --> 29:37.107
Liv...
And a lot of people,

29:37.109 --> 29:39.443
A lot
of anonymous internet people,

29:39.445 --> 29:41.478
Cowards who won't use
their names,

29:41.480 --> 29:42.980
Apparently want
to have me killed.

29:42.982 --> 29:44.548
Also raped.

29:44.550 --> 29:47.084
How come whenever a woman does
something that people don't like

29:47.086 --> 29:49.186
The only way
these men on the internet

29:49.188 --> 29:51.522
Know how to express themselves
is by threatening rape?

29:51.524 --> 29:53.056
Listen.
Turn off the computer, liv.

29:53.058 --> 29:54.291
No, seriously.

29:54.293 --> 29:56.126
I have...

29:56.128 --> 30:01.098
At least 1,000 threats
of rape here,

30:01.100 --> 30:03.367
Just on this one site,

30:03.369 --> 30:06.303
From guys who are mad
that i had the audacity

30:06.305 --> 30:08.438
To be born
female and black.

30:08.440 --> 30:09.439
Olivia...

30:09.441 --> 30:10.574
Turn off the computer.

30:10.576 --> 30:14.211
Do you think
if i told them i own a gun

30:14.213 --> 30:17.281
And that i've shot someone,
they'd threaten to rape me?

30:17.283 --> 30:18.515
Do you think if i told them

30:18.517 --> 30:21.485
I've survived
being kidnapped and tortured,

30:21.487 --> 30:24.488
They would get that
their weak little misspellings

30:24.490 --> 30:25.923
Barely make me blink?

30:25.925 --> 30:27.991
That i would welcome
the chance

30:27.993 --> 30:31.261
To take out
a little bit of ptsd

30:31.263 --> 30:33.130
On the next man
who put his hands on me?

30:33.132 --> 30:34.298
You think
they'd still want to --

30:34.300 --> 30:36.366
Turn off the computer now,

30:36.368 --> 30:37.885
Or i will come over there,

30:37.886 --> 30:39.403
Walk through all the reporters
outside your building,

30:39.405 --> 30:41.205
And turn it off for you.

30:45.845 --> 30:49.046
[ breathes deeply ]

30:59.158 --> 31:00.290
[ sobs ]

31:00.292 --> 31:01.792
[ voice breaking ]
i'm fine.

31:01.794 --> 31:04.595
I'm just...

31:04.597 --> 31:08.365
I'm losing it,
but only a little bit.

31:08.367 --> 31:11.301
[ laughs ]

31:11.303 --> 31:14.171
I'm fine.

31:19.912 --> 31:22.512
[<i> camera shutter clicking</i> ]

31:22.514 --> 31:25.449
♪♪

31:28.254 --> 31:29.653
[ knocking ]

31:29.655 --> 31:33.090
[ monitor beeping ]

31:33.092 --> 31:34.524
How's that arm?

31:34.526 --> 31:36.026
Flesh wound.

31:36.028 --> 31:37.961
You've seen me take worse.

31:37.963 --> 31:40.597
I'm sorry for getting you
involved in this.

31:40.599 --> 31:42.132
If i knew
you'd get hurt --

31:42.134 --> 31:44.268
I never showed up
at grand central station.

31:45.638 --> 31:48.105
We're spies.

31:48.107 --> 31:50.574
There's no forever for us.

31:50.576 --> 31:52.542
We both knew that.

31:52.544 --> 31:54.678
And what about now?

31:54.680 --> 31:57.414
What about now?

31:57.416 --> 32:01.318
Come back to the states
with me.

32:06.158 --> 32:08.125
[<i> camera shutter clicking</i> ]

32:08.127 --> 32:11.128
Those senators
came to<i> you!</i>

32:11.130 --> 32:13.330
They're deferring to you.

32:13.332 --> 32:15.399
They're bowing down.
What should that tell you?

32:15.401 --> 32:17.601
That's it time to come out
from behind the throne

32:17.603 --> 32:20.470
And wield some power
that's got your name on it!

32:20.472 --> 32:22.139
I won't do it, cyrus.

32:22.141 --> 32:24.141
As much as i want to,
there's no way

32:24.143 --> 32:25.609
That i come out of this
looking like anything more

32:25.611 --> 32:26.643
Than a vindictive harpy.

32:26.645 --> 32:28.245
The smart play --

32:28.247 --> 32:31.114
The smart play
is to take the high road.

32:31.116 --> 32:32.983
You know that.

32:34.186 --> 32:36.954
What that man did
to you...

32:36.956 --> 32:38.388
What he did to us...

32:38.390 --> 32:40.123
Is on
completely different levels.

32:40.125 --> 32:41.491
Cyrus, come on.

32:41.493 --> 32:43.427
He was my husband.

32:43.429 --> 32:46.630
You were just colleagues,
friends.

32:46.632 --> 32:49.132
Why are so hell-bent
on revenge?

32:49.134 --> 32:51.101
Let it go already.

32:51.103 --> 32:53.570
C-colleagues.
[ sighs ]

32:53.572 --> 32:55.305
Friends.

32:55.307 --> 32:58.608
Mellie, i devoted my life
to him, to you,

32:58.610 --> 33:00.043
To the grant cause.

33:00.045 --> 33:03.413
The last 14 years
have been...

33:03.415 --> 33:05.148
[ breathes deeply ]

33:05.150 --> 33:07.250
[ scoffs ]

33:07.252 --> 33:09.453
He kicked in the teeth
and didn't even look back,

33:09.455 --> 33:11.321
And i'm supposed
to just it go?

33:11.323 --> 33:14.291
I guess that's the difference
between me and you, cy.

33:14.293 --> 33:16.126
When my heart is broken,

33:16.128 --> 33:18.061
I can get up
and dust myself off

33:18.063 --> 33:20.364
And walk away
with some dignity.

33:20.366 --> 33:21.631
[ sighs ]

33:21.633 --> 33:23.533
Dignity's a good visual.

33:25.371 --> 33:27.537
That's -- that's what
you think the difference is?

33:27.539 --> 33:29.139
Between you and me?
No, no.

33:29.141 --> 33:30.374
There difference
between you and me

33:30.376 --> 33:31.675
Is that your heart
was never broken

33:31.677 --> 33:34.178
Because you never loved him.

33:34.179 --> 33:36.680
You needed him, used him,
coexisted with him,

33:36.682 --> 33:38.315
But you did not love him!

33:38.317 --> 33:40.584
I would have died
for that man.

33:40.586 --> 33:43.186
I loved him as my son...

33:43.188 --> 33:44.454
As my child...

33:44.456 --> 33:47.090
As my soul.

33:47.092 --> 33:49.526
That does not end.
That never ends.

33:49.528 --> 33:52.696
It just rips a hole inside
of you that never closes.

33:52.698 --> 33:54.398
Your child is dead!

33:54.400 --> 33:56.733
You can visit his grave,
bring him flowers.

33:56.735 --> 33:59.102
You know exactly where he is
and what he is.

33:59.104 --> 34:01.471
My child
is breathing and talking

34:01.473 --> 34:04.107
Right down the block from me
at 1600 pennsylvania avenue,

34:04.109 --> 34:05.275
But i can't see him.

34:05.277 --> 34:07.644
I don't know how he is
or what he needs

34:07.646 --> 34:08.745
Or if he's even okay.

34:08.747 --> 34:10.414
He's surrounded by vultures

34:10.416 --> 34:12.449
Who want to pick the flesh
from his bones,

34:12.451 --> 34:15.052
But he doesn't know it.

34:15.054 --> 34:16.787
And i do.

34:16.789 --> 34:19.689
And i'm not there
to shelter him from the storms,

34:19.691 --> 34:24.628
To pick up after him, to remove
the obstacles in his path.

34:24.630 --> 34:28.732
Your child
is safe in the ground

34:28.734 --> 34:31.701
Where everything bad
has already happened.

34:31.703 --> 34:36.073
But my child -- my soul --

34:36.075 --> 34:38.408
All you have to do
is turn on the news

34:38.410 --> 34:40.410
To see that the bad things
for him

34:40.412 --> 34:41.378
Are just getting started.

34:41.380 --> 34:44.281
Get out...

34:44.283 --> 34:47.784
Before i have you thrown out.

34:47.786 --> 34:51.121
Oh, no need, no need.

34:52.391 --> 34:54.624
I quit.

34:54.626 --> 34:57.094
[ door slams ]

35:01.800 --> 35:03.366
Bribery, treason,
high crimes and misdemeanors.

35:03.368 --> 35:04.734
These are the charges
for impeachment,

35:04.736 --> 35:06.470
According to our constitution.

35:06.472 --> 35:10.273
Just which of them, if any,
will president grant face?

35:10.275 --> 35:12.242
Within minutes
of ms. Pope's declaration,

35:12.244 --> 35:15.112
Pundits began postulating
how, and if,

35:15.114 --> 35:17.380
Grant broke the law
with his affair.

35:17.382 --> 35:18.815
[<i> projector running</i> ]

35:18.817 --> 35:20.717
Reporter: Are you gonna respond
to allegations?

35:20.719 --> 35:22.219
Sal:
Where is olivia pope?

35:22.221 --> 35:23.470
When's she
coming out of hiding?

35:23.471 --> 35:24.720
Just tell us
why she won't defend herself

35:24.723 --> 35:26.490
As passionately
as she defends her clients.

35:26.492 --> 35:28.291
She's usually
so well-spoken.

35:28.293 --> 35:30.627
[ camera shutters clicking ]

35:30.629 --> 35:32.696
[ sighs ]

35:32.698 --> 35:33.864
"for a black woman."

35:36.568 --> 35:38.668
"she's usually so well-spoken
for a black woman."

35:38.670 --> 35:40.604
Isn't that what you meant?

35:40.606 --> 35:43.340
<i> I say that because i've been</i>
<i> looking at the last 72 hours</i>

35:43.342 --> 35:44.841
<i> Of your station's</i>
<i> news coverage,</i>

35:44.843 --> 35:46.326
<i> And when you're not suggesting</i>

35:46.327 --> 35:47.810
<i> That olivia pope</i>
<i> is an angry black woman,</i>

35:47.813 --> 35:49.446
<i> You're implying</i>
<i> she's a homewrecker</i>

35:49.448 --> 35:50.680
<i> Who slept her way to the top.</i>

35:50.682 --> 35:52.182
[<i> indistinct shouting</i> ]

35:52.184 --> 35:54.384
Quinn:
What the hell was that?

35:54.386 --> 35:55.919
Gladiating.
You did the exact opposite
of what i asked.

35:55.921 --> 35:57.254
You can only dodge so long.

35:57.256 --> 35:58.555
At some point,
you have to throw a punch.

35:58.557 --> 35:59.723
You went off-script.

35:59.725 --> 36:02.459
This...Is...War.

36:02.461 --> 36:03.660
There is no script.

36:03.662 --> 36:05.295
You can choose the battle,

36:05.297 --> 36:07.264
But if you send me out,
i'm fighting my way.

36:07.266 --> 36:08.798
I don't play.
I don't hide.

36:08.800 --> 36:10.400
I don't hold back
or look for exits,

36:10.402 --> 36:12.269
And i sure as hell don't lean
on the ropes and take it.

36:12.271 --> 36:14.204
I swing because that's me.

36:14.206 --> 36:17.207
That's who i am.
That is how i gladiate.

36:17.209 --> 36:20.177
[ aretha franklin's "(i can't
get no) satisfaction" plays ]

36:23.582 --> 36:25.465
They're gonna try
to confuse you.

36:25.466 --> 36:27.349
They will bring up your past
criminal record to rattle you.

36:27.352 --> 36:28.718
When you get stuck
or don't know what to say,

36:28.720 --> 36:31.188
Just accuse them of playing
dog-whistle politics.

36:31.190 --> 36:33.190
Now, quinn perkins
wasn't always your name.

36:33.192 --> 36:34.958
Before you started working
for ms. Pope,

36:34.960 --> 36:36.426
You were known
as lindsay dwyer.

36:36.428 --> 36:37.694
The "molotov mistress."

36:37.696 --> 36:39.296
That's what you were
going for, right, dan?

36:39.298 --> 36:40.797
But why would you
bring that up now

36:40.799 --> 36:42.432
When we're supposed to be
talking about...

36:42.434 --> 36:44.734
Olivia pope doesn't fit with
the slutty-mistress stereotype.

36:44.736 --> 36:46.636
So instead of representing her
as she is --

36:46.638 --> 36:47.837
A formidable,
passionate advocate --

36:47.839 --> 36:49.606
You take the easy route,
shading her,

36:49.608 --> 36:51.241
Using all manner
of coded language.

36:51.243 --> 36:52.909
There's a name for that,
claire, and it's...

36:52.911 --> 36:54.411
Dog-whistle politics.

36:54.413 --> 36:56.446
That's your buzzword.
That's your talking point.

36:56.448 --> 36:57.981
Dog-whistle politics.

36:57.983 --> 36:59.783
Yeah, okay,
but what exactly is that?

36:59.785 --> 37:02.886
It's racism, sexism,
anti-semitism, misogyny.

37:02.888 --> 37:05.422
It's bigotry in the form
of a language so coded that...

37:05.424 --> 37:07.557
Only the person it's targeting
is insulted by it,

37:07.559 --> 37:09.492
Like a dog whistle.
It lets them get away
with it.

37:09.494 --> 37:12.495
Are you accusing me
of using offensive language?
Yes.

37:12.497 --> 37:13.997
On this network alone,
olivia pope

37:13.999 --> 37:15.532
Has been described
as lucky...

37:15.534 --> 37:16.733
...Sassy, ambitious...

37:16.735 --> 37:18.668
...Well-spoken,
well-mannered, articulate...

37:18.670 --> 37:21.738
...Shrill, calculating,
overconfident, secretive...

37:21.740 --> 37:23.273
...Urban, hot-blooded...

37:23.275 --> 37:24.641
...Known to use
thug politics...

37:24.643 --> 37:26.243
...Arrogant, a siren.

37:26.245 --> 37:28.478
Words like these mean nothing
to the general public,

37:28.480 --> 37:29.779
Which is why the media --

37:29.781 --> 37:31.581
And i'm including you in there,
claire --

37:31.583 --> 37:32.782
Can get away
with using them.

37:32.784 --> 37:34.985
But when women of color,
like ms. Pope,

